outputs.output_descr: Project is designed to strengthen skills, knowledge, and technology capacity of public and private sector support giving institutions and SMEs.  It will also strengthen Government's policy review and regulatory capacity as well as cluster development and competiveness   through value addition in prioritized GTP sectors mainly in leather and metal industries.
